🔗 HOW POLYGON IS USED (IMPORTANT)

Polygon is the brain of access control.

1️⃣ Smart Contract Stores:

File ID (hash / CID reference)

Access rules

Price

Expiry timestamp

Download limits

Owner address

2️⃣ Payment Handling

Users pay smart contract

Contract verifies amount

Funds auto-split:

Creator

Platform fee (if any)

3️⃣ Access Verification

Before file decryption:

if (block.timestamp < expiry && downloads < limit && paid == true)
   allowAccess();

4️⃣ NFT Access Keys (Advanced)

Creator can mint “Access NFT”

Only NFT holders can download

NFT can be:

Transferable

Time-bound

Single-use

5️⃣ Audit & Proof

Anyone can verify:

When file was uploaded

That it wasn’t modified

Polygon transaction = proof

